因素”。 （2024）： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg" width="384" height="635" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:635,&quot;width&quot;:384,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:72283,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3a10f7c7-48b1-442c-b9d1-227177678e32_384x635.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.economist.com/science-and-technology/2024/06/12/china-has-become-a-scientific-superpower">经济学人</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>医疗保健非常棒，中国通过浏览健康支出而造成伤害。但是，应用的物理科学是美国希望培养的面向出口高科技产业（计算机芯片，电动汽车等）的关键输入。应用物理科学对于<em>赢得战争</em>也至关重要，这对于建造大量高度准确和破坏性的导弹和其他武器等等。经济学家当然认为军事力量是中国科学推动的重要因素：</p><blockquote><p>中国共产党（CCP）进行了农业研究（这是确保该国<a href="https://www.economist.com/china/2023/07/13/china-is-obsessed-with-food-security-climate-change-will-challenge-it">粮食安全</a>的关键 - 科学家的首要任务……工程学是现代的最终中国纪律，”我认为这是部分是关于军事技术的，部分是因为这是发展一个国家所需的。”</p></blockquote><p>因此，在物理科学中加强美国的能力似乎是一个好主意，这不仅是因为它改善了世界并提高了我们的GDP，而且还可以帮助保持美国及其盟友的强大。</p><h4>我们实际上可以获得更多的联邦科学资金吗？</h4><p>关于科学资金的讨论通常集中在联邦政府上。这部分是因为当您希望改变某些东西时，政府资金只是最简单的政策杠杆。这也是因为政府资金是美国研究生态系统的薄弱环节。随着时间的流逝，美国私营部门的研发支出一直在稳步上升，而政府对科学的资金则无情地成为GDP的一部分： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f97c7a-ef4d-4fec-87b0-d012352c9f0c_929x393.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f97c7a-ef4d-4fec-87b0-d012352c9f0c_929x393.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f97c7a-ef4d-4fec-87b0-d012352c9f0c_929x393.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f97c7a-ef4d-4fec-87b0-d012352c9f0c_929x393.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f97c7a-ef4d-4fec-87b0-d012352c9f0c_929x393.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f97c7a-ef4d-4fec-87b0-d012352c9f0c_929x393.jpeg" width="929" height="393" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b2f97c7a-ef4d-4fec-87b0-d012352c9f0c